/**
 * RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) Module
 *
 * Complete RAG system for building AI applications with document knowledge:
 *
 * Features:
 * - Document ingestion with intelligent chunking
 * - Multi-provider embeddings (OpenAI, Anthropic)
 * - Vector storage with pgvector
 * - Semantic and hybrid search
 * - Context-aware LLM generation
 * - Streaming responses
 * - Token tracking for billing
 *
 * Quick Start:
 * ```ts
 * // 1. Ingest documents
 * await ingestDocument({
 *   content: 'Your document content...',
 *   metadata: { source: 'upload', title: 'Guide' },
 * });
 *
 * // 2. Query with RAG
 * const response = await queryRAG({
 *   query: 'How do I get started?',
 *   userId: 'user-123',
 * });
 *
 * console.log(response.answer);
 * console.log(response.sources);
 * ```
 *
 * @module integrations/ai/rag
 */

